@startuml 借阅
left to right direction

' 定义状态
state 初始
state "借阅中\n(borrowed)" as Borrowed
state "续借" as Renew
state "逾期\n(overdue)" as Overdue
state "已归还\n(returned)" as Returned

' 初始到借阅中
[*] --> 初始
初始 --> Borrowed : 借出

' 借阅中 ⇄ 续借
Borrowed --> Renew : 发起续借
Renew --> Borrowed : 续借成功

' 续借 → 逾期
Renew --> Overdue : 超出续借期限

' 借阅中 → 逾期（直接逾期）
Borrowed --> Overdue : 到期未还

' 逾期 → 已归还
Overdue --> Returned : 归还

' 已归还为结束状态
Returned --> [*]

@enduml